]
},
"children":[
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"f818e2",
"children":[
"Bronchitis, bronchogenic carcinoma, and bronchiectasis are the most common causes of hemoptysis."
]
},
{
"type":"heading",
"class":"tricked",
"children":[
"Don't Be Tricked"
]
},
{
"type":"list",
"class":"tricked",
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"list-item",
"hlId":"252a0b",
"children":[
"Confirm that a patient has hemoptysis rather than epistaxis or ",
{
"type":"abbreviation",
"title":"gastrointestinal",
"children":[
"GI"
]
},
" bleeding; then check the platelet count and coagulation parameters."
]
},
" "
]
},
{
